body:
If folks have opted into sharing analytics, we should log framework errors.

To start we can use a string-based error ID.  Once we have some data, we can evaluate whether that's sufficient and amenable for data analysis.

/cc @jacob314 @InMatrix

comment_data.body: We'll know more re: this bug later today.
@pq do you know if we're getting these framework errors reported to us now?
Not yet.  This is part of the structured error work which is just now revving back up.

milestone.description: Work triaged but not yet planned for a specific release.
milestone.title: Backlog

title: report logged flutter errors to analytics
